posts.post_content: Looking to build a Senators player set. I’m looking for cards in low grades, but with nicer eye appeal. Already have Unglaub. Email me at [url]cjgammer@gmail.com[/url]

Also looking for a low low grade 206 WaJo, doesn’t matter which one. My budget for is 250/300 

Thanks
Update: Now have Unglaub, Elberfeld, and Johnson thanks to Rob G.

In addition looking for a poor condition George Brown (Washington) I'm looking to spend 120ish on one. Thanks

Curt

I still need Tannehill, Street, Browne, Milan, Schaefer,  Groom, Delehanty, Conroy, and Ganley. 

Thanks
Curt

Just Got Gray, Schaefer (Washington), from Kris.

Curt
Still need Tannehill, Brown, Delahanty, and Groom! I’m so close to being finished with the set! My first T206 card set ever and a inaugural cornerstone to card collecting for me!

Delehanty, J Tannehill, and Groom needed. 80% done and these last three are arguably more common than the rest. Looking for worn cards, no paper loss or pin holes, and not altered. If you have one or more of those cards with some honest wear, please contact me at above email. Willing to pay fair prices or at least as fair as the quarantine blues will let me. 
Thank you,
Curt 
:)

 A Appreciation post for the wonderful people who helped me along the way has been already posted. We are close to the victory lap!
